1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:18,600
At the heart of our practice is the development of the silent mind.

2
00:00:18,600 --> 00:00:28,320
It is a practical method to reduce fluctuations of consciousness and cultivate a profound

3
00:00:28,320 --> 00:00:39,960
sense of stability and self consolidation. It starts from a basic observation. Most

4
00:00:39,960 --> 00:00:49,960
of us spend the day constantly engaging with many objects and many thoughts. It causes

5
00:00:49,960 --> 00:01:03,080
our mental, emotional and physical potential to be divided into a thousand things.

6
00:01:03,080 --> 00:01:14,040
In silent mind, we bring consciousness back to ourselves and develop a sense of wholeness

7
00:01:14,040 --> 00:01:29,960
and self consolidation. We reduce random mind wandering through self awareness and

8
00:01:29,960 --> 00:01:42,160
sustained attention. Even short moments of this state can enhance

9
00:01:42,160 --> 00:01:58,800
our clarity and sense of inner fulfillment. With continued practice, we can live better

10
00:01:58,800 --> 00:02:09,360
by transforming from within and empowering for a lifetime yourself and the others.

